high_descs: Turn to the left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and step forward to face the microwave.
Cut the apple in the fridge into three pieces.
Turn around and step forward and turn left to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the top shelf on the left side of the fridge.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Pick up a piece of apple in the microwave.
Turn around and step forward and face the fridge to the left.
Cool the apple piece in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn around and cross the room, turn right and cross the room and turn right to face the trash can.
Place the apple piece in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Cool a piece of apple and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter with the coffee maker.
Pick up the gray knife in front of the coffee maker.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Cut the apple inside the microwave.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Place the knife inside the freezer.
Turn left and go back to the microwave.
Take a piece of apple out of the microwave.
Turn around to go back to the refrigerator.
Chill the apple inside the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn around and go to the other side of the counter.
Place the apple inside the black trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a chilled piece of cut apple.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter by the coffee maker and toaster.
Pick up a knife from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and cut the apple inside the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the knife inside.
Walk back to the microwave.
Take a piece of the apple out of the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Set the apple inside the refrigerator.  Open the refrigerator and take the apple out.
Turn around and walk across the room.  Turn right to go to the trash can.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled piece of apple in the trash can.
